# Session [Network] – Network+

## Main Topics
- Network chist? (What is a network?)
- PC ha baraye ertebat be ham be che chizi niaz darand? (What PCs need communicate to eachother ?)

## Flashback – Network Types
- **PAN (Personal Area Network)** – shabake ye fardi, mesl Bluetooth ya USB
- **LAN (Local Area Network)** – shabake mahali, masalan toye khane ya office
- **WAN (Wide Area Network)** – shabake bozorg, masalan Internet
- **CAN (Campus Area Network)** – shabake campus ya daneshgoh kheyly bozorg

## Explanation
- Network = be 2 ya bishtar PC ke be ham vasl mishavand
- PC = har device ke CPU dashte bashad
- dar PC ha baraye resource rad v badal kardan be ham ertebat barqarar mikonand
- Baraye ertebat niaz be **hardware** va **software** hast:
  - **Hardware** = Cart shabake, kabel, switch, router
  - **Software** = Zaban narm afzari moshtarak (masalan TCP/IP) ke PC ha baraye ertebat estefade mikonand

